# My Website Rules

## DEV SERVER POLICY (HARD RULE)

This rule is mandatory for every task in this repo.

- NEVER run two dev servers for this project in parallel.
- NEVER keep two localhost ports active for the same app.
- ALWAYS verify existing running server(s) before any `npm run dev`.
- ALWAYS use and share one canonical URL only: `http://localhost:5173/My-website/`.

## Required Startup Checklist (must follow in order)

1. Check active terminals/processes for `vite` or `npm run dev`.
2. If one healthy server already exists, reuse it and do not start a new one.
3. If duplicates exist, stop all duplicates first.
4. Start exactly one server instance.
5. Confirm and report one active URL only.

## Forbidden (no exceptions unless user explicitly requests)

- Starting a second server "for testing".
- Leaving `5173` and `5174` running at the same time.
- Running a fresh server without checking existing processes first.
